{
  "chapter": 73,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十三回\"人性无善恶\"围绕李寻欢、孙小红和林仙儿三人同行的旅程展开。林仙儿请求去看阿飞，孙小红虽然不屑但最终允许。途中，孙小红与李寻欢深入对话，讨论了上官金虹敬酒的深意、人性本无善恶的哲理、以及如何把握战机与克制冲动。孙小红向李寻欢坦白了心迹，指出他\"宁可被人恨也不愿被人爱\"的心理。抵达阿飞的小屋后，林仙儿恳求再见阿飞一面，李寻欢最终心软答应。本章以细腻的人物心理刻画见长，展现了李寻欢的仁义与无奈、孙小红的率真勇敢、以及林仙儿的悔恨与脆弱。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我们走我们的，你走你的，你为什么要跟来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我也想去看看阿飞。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你还要看他干什么？难道你害他害得还不够惨？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只想……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我们不会让他再看见你的，你去了也是白去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只想远远看他一眼，他要不要看我都没关系。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "腿长在你自己身上，你一定跟着来，我们也没法子，只不过……你既然跟着来了，就莫要后悔。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我做事从不后悔。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你看，我早就算准她会跟着来的，果然没有算错。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你本来就要她跟来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "当然要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我刚才既然已没法子再对她下手，就只好等下一次机会，她若不跟着我们来，我哪有机会？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "其实你根本不必等，刚才也可以下手，无论她说什么，你都可以不听。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你们男子汉讲的是'话出如风，一诺千金'，难道我们女人就可以说了话当放屁么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "但你怎知她会跟着来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为她想要我们保护她，她跟'小李探花'在一起时，无论谁想杀她，也没这个胆子下手的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "说得好听些，这就叫做狐假虎威，说得难听些，这就叫做狗仗人势。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "这两种说法好像都不大好听。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你若是做了这些事，无论别人话说得多难听，也只好听听了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知不知道龙啸云要跟上官金虹结拜的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "听说过……你们就是为这件事来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "嗯，因为我们知道在这里一定可以遇到很多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "最主要的，当然还是因为我知道可以在这里遇见你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "若不是你们来，说不定我已……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "说不定上官金虹已进了棺材。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "其实对上官金虹那种人，你本不必讲道义，你若在他看到上官飞尸体的时候出手，一定可以杀了他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "只怕未必。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "未必？你认为他看到自己儿子死了，心也不会乱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "血浓于水，上官金虹多少也有点人性。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么你为何不出手？你要知道，你对他讲交情，他可不会对你讲交情。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我和他现在已势不两立，谁也不会对谁讲交情。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我不出手，只因为我还要等更好的机会。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "在我看来，那时已经是最好的机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你看错了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "看到自己的儿子死了，心虽然会乱，但心里却会生出种悲愤之气，那时我若出手，他就会将这股怒气发泄在我身上！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "人在悲愤中，不但力量要比平时大得多，勇气也要平时大得多，那时上官金虹若出手，一击之威，我实在没有把握能接得住。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "原来你也不是我想像中那样的人，有时你也会用心机的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我若真像别人想得那么好，至少已死了八十次。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上官金虹若知道你的意思，一定会后悔喝那杯酒的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他绝不后悔。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "因为我的意思他本就很明了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么，他为什么还要敬你酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他敬我那杯酒，为的并不是我对他讲道义——讲道义的人在他眼中看来，简直是呆子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么他为的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "因为他已明了我的意思，知道我并不是呆子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他知道你也和他一样，能等，能忍，能把握机会，也能判断什么时候才是最好的机会，所以才敬你的酒，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他觉得你也和他是同样的人，所以才佩服你，欣赏你——一个人最欣赏的人，本就必定是和他自己同样的人。因为每个人都一定很欣赏自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "这句话说得很好，简直不像你这种年纪的人能说得出来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你真的和他是同样的人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "从某些方面说，是的，只不过因为我们生长的环境不同，遇着的人和事也不同，所以才会造成完全不同的两个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "有人说：人性本善，也有人说，人性本恶，在我看来，人性本无善恶，一个人是善是恶，都是后天的影响。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "看来你不但很了解别人，也很了解自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "一个人若要真的完全了解自己，并不容易。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "一个人若要了解自己，必定要先经过很多折磨，尝过很多痛苦——是不是？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这么说来，我倒希望永远不要了解自己了，了解得越多，痛苦越多，完全不了解，也许反倒幸运些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "上官金虹敬我酒的时候，你们还在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我们已经走了，这件事都是我以后听人说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在你和上官金虹都是了不起的大人物，你们的一举一动，在别人看来都是大消息，今天晚上，在这城里，至少也有十万人在谈论你……你信不信？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "所以我才佩服你爷爷，身若浮云，心如止水，随心所欲，无牵无挂，这种人才真的是了不起！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他老人家的确已什么事都看穿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知不知道那口棺材是谁送去的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我猜不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "送棺材去的，难道就是杀上官飞的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "想必就是他，因为知道上官飞尸体在哪里的人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "因为他想打击上官金虹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他也恨上官金虹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "也许他并不是恨，他想打击上官金虹，也许只因为上官金虹被打倒后，他才有机会去救他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我更不懂了，他既然想救他，为何又要打击他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "也许他是要上官金虹后悔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "人的心，实在比什么事都难了解。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不错，世上最难了解的，就是人心和人性，人性的复杂，远在天下任何一种武功之上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "但你若不能了解人性，武功也就永远无法达到巅峰，因为无论什么事，都是和人性息息相关的，武功也不例外。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我什么都不想了解，只想了解你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你却好像很怕被人了解，所以时时刻刻都在防备着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "怕？怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "怕别人爱上你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为你知道无论谁若是真正地了解了你，一定就会忍不住要爱上你的，你宁可被人恨，也不愿被人爱，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "现在的年代的确变了，以前的小姑娘，嘴里绝不会说出'爱'这个字。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "以后的小姑娘也未必敢说，可是我……我无论生在哪个年代，就算是生在几百年以前，只要是我心里想说的话，我还是一样会说出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这地方你认得的，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "阿飞已回来了？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你是不是也想进去看看他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我……我可以进去么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这本是你的家，你要进去就进去，本不必问别人的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "可是，现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "现在当然不同了，你自己也该知道，这种情况是谁造成的？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你本可在这里快快活活、安安静静地过一生，可是你自己不愿意，因为你看不起这个家，也看不起这个人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我才知道自己错了，我还能够活着，全都是因为他在保护我，若是没有他，我也许早就被人杀了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和他在一起的时候，没有人敢来伤我一根头发……但现在，好像任何人都可以来要我的命……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你以为他还会像以前那样保护你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我不知道，我也不在乎……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我只想再见他一面，对他说两句话，然后立刻就走，这要求无论怎么都不过分，你们总可以答应我吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我并不是不答应，只可惜你说的话很难令人相信。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "就算我到时候又不肯走了，你们也可以赶我走的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "这也许就是我最后一次见他了，以后他若知道你们连最后一面都不让我去见他一次，会恨你们一辈子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你只说两句话？说完了立刻就走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我难道真的那么不知趣？难道真要等你们来赶我走？只要你们答应我这最后的一个要求，我死而无怨。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让她去吧，无论如何，两句话总害不了人的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 465
    }
